data.description: This beautiful 2-story floorplan features 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathroom with a 2 car garage built in 2020. Open floor plan, large living room, granite countertops, beautiful island, carpet in living room and bedroom on first floor, spacious rooms, high ceilings, media room/office space upstairs, jack and jill bathroom connecting rooms upstairs. Located in a cul-de-sac! This home is perfect for entertaining guests. Home is located right off Culebra and Ingram near 410. Close to Ingram Park mall and Lackland Airforce Base. It's a MUST SEE! (washer/dryer, and fridge do not convey.)
